BCG获Vault職業出版评为全球第二高声望的[[管理諮詢|管理諮詢]]公司。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vault.com/wps/portal/usa/rankings/individual?rankingId1=77&rankingId2=-1&rankings=1&regionId=0&rankingYear=2013 |title=Vault Most Prestigious Consulting Company |access-date=2012-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226233511/http://www.vault.com/wps/portal/usa/rankings/individual?rankingId1=77&rankingId2=-1&rankings=1&regionId=0&rankingYear=2013 |archive-date=2012-12-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在[[財星雜誌|財星雜誌]]2012年全球「百大最佳企業雇主」排行榜中排行第二。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/best-companies/2012/full_list/ |title=100 Best Companies to Work For 2012: Full list - from FORTUNE |access-date=2012-11-25 |archive-date=2012-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031135647/http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/best-companies/2012/full_list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2012年获[[CNN|CNN]]选为工商管理碩士的第五佳雇主。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://money.cnn.com/galleries/2012/pf/jobs/1205/gallery.top-MBA-employers/5.html |title=Top MBA Employers |access-date=2012-12-12 |archive-date=2019-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620112152/https://money.cnn.com/galleries/2012/pf/jobs/1205/gallery.top-MBA-employers/5.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

